'''Malubi''' was the [[malvil-tree]] bound to the family of the [[Xamster/Legends|Xamster]] [[Xeran]] on [[Xagobah/Legends|Xagobah]]. It was a hundred [[Meter/Legends|meters]] tall and had lived for a thousand [[Standard year/Legends|years]]. Malubi's spores allowed the young [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] to enter into [[Wat Tambor/Legends|Wat Tambor's]] [[Mazariyan]] Citadel. Malubi had various tendrils that stemmed from its fungus stalk. These tendrils could detect body temperature and heart rate.

